Paper: hep-th/0112171

Date: 2001-12-19

Title: Nonlinear Constraints from Non-Abelian Internal Symmetries

Authors: Ludwik Turko

Comments: 4 pages, to appear in Nuclear Physics Proceedings Supplement

STATISTICAL QCD, held at Bielefeld August 2001Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. A702 (2002) 361-365

Symmetry invariant local interaction of a many body system leads to globalconstraints. We obtain explicit forms of the global macroscopic conditionassuring that at the microscopic level the evolution respects the overallsymmetry.